data.description: Stunning 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bathroom Waterfront Brick Home on Brices CreekWelcome to your waterfront oasis! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom brick home on Brices Creek offers the perfect blend of comfort, elegance, and outdoor paradise. From the moment you enter through the door, you'll be captivated by the exceptional features and scenic views this property has to offer. The heart of this home is the generous living room, complete with a cozy gas logs fireplace, perfect for those chilly evenings and gatherings with loved ones. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring beautiful white countertops, a convenient breakfast bar, an inviting eat-in area, and an abundance of cabinet space for all your culinary needs. Just off the kitchen, there's a formal dining room that adds a touch of elegance to your dining experiences, making it ideal for special occasions and dinner parties. The owner's suite is a true retreat with two vanities, a walk-in shower, and a relaxing jetted tub. It's a perfect space to unwind and rejuvenate. Upstairs, discover a versatile flex space that can be tailored to your needs - whether it's a home office, guest room, or a personal home gym. Head outside and indulge in the outdoor amenities. A screened-in porch offers a peaceful spot to enjoy your morning coffee or a sunset cocktail. The in-ground swimming pool is perfect for cooling off on hot summer days, and the private dock out to Brices Creek is your gateway to water activities such as boating and swimming. USE caution when walking on the dock, not all boards are secure! This home is strategically situated, providing easy access to Historic Downtown New Bern, Coastal Carolina Regional Airport, and Carolina East Medical Center. Whether you're looking for entertainment, travel convenience, or healthcare services, you're just a short drive away from all the essentials. Don't miss the opportunity to make this waterfront dream home your own. Call us today to schedule your private tour!
